ISLAMABAD, May 12 (APP): Indus River System Authority (IRSA) convened an emergency meeting on Monday to discuss review of water situation, T 5 progress and operational constraint of Tarbela Dam at 1470 feet.
Chairman IRSA will preside over the meeting while all other authority members and concerned officials will attend it, said a press release here Sunday.
